game.name: Move Here Move There
game.description:
Participating in complex puzzle challenges will help to sharpen your brain and boost your logical skills. Today we have brought to you a brand new arcade game where you have to put your logic analysis and concentration abilities to the test. Are you ready to try it out right away? Join Move Here Move There and get ready to move the light beam from the dark blue tile right to the green target tile! Create a path using the boxes that include plenty of steps and directions!

Put your fingers on your mouse or tap the screen to swap and move a block to the correct tile to make your way! You would have two modes Classic and Endless to choose from in this free html5 brain teasing game. Select the board size or difficulty level in Classic or Endless mode! There are plenty of puzzles to deal with in the Endless mode. There are chances of meeting with a new puzzle every time when you visit since these challenges are procedurally generated. 

In classic mode, you would find multiple difficulty levels including 4X4, 5X5, 6X6 and 7X7. Use your mouse to move the light blue tiles around by clicking and dragging in this lovely arcade challenge! You would see the numbers in the boxes that will tell you how many squares the beam is able to move when it collides with that particular tile and know the direction using the arrows. In case if you realize that your path is perfect to move on, click play to watch it move. Good luck to finish all the puzzle solving skills to complete each level!
